<div>
<p>
<measure quantity="9" unit="months">
<num value="9">九</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>
<num value="45">戊申</num>
<pc>，</pc>成景俊拔魏睢陵<pc>。</pc>
<num value="55">戊午</num>
<pc>，</pc>北<placeName>兗州</placeName>
